Dr. Ankit Pandey is a Neuro Psychiatrist. Possessing special skills, interest & experience in chronic headache, body ache, and other neurological pain along with prolonged weakness in the body. He also has concern and experience in treating all forms of sleep disturbance in various age groups, all types of sexual problems/dysfunction, any difficulty in concentration & memory. Apart from this, his major areas of interest are child, adolescent & geriatric psychiatric problems (Psychotic, anxiety spectrum, mood, stress-related somatoform, conversion/ hysteria disorders). De-Addiction from Alcohol, Tobacco, Cannabis, Opold, Sleeping Pills & other substances are other interests & concerns. Dr. Pandey has the vision to create awareness for mental health within the general population & provide special care, attention, help & treatment for all forms of neuropsychiatric illness.
